      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2444870-ai-models-cant-learn-as-they-go-along-like-humans-do/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在初始训练阶段之后，人工智能算法无法更新和学习新数据，这意味着科技公司必须从头开始训练新模型]]></description>
