      <title>吃肉真的会增加患 2 型糖尿病的风险吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2444648-does-eating-meat-really-raise-your-risk-of-type-2-diabetes/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
